Complete picture of a type or method (members + callers + callees + related)

Usage: kodex info [OPTIONS] <FQN>

Arguments:
  <FQN>  Symbol FQN (from search results)

Options:
      --exclude <EXCLUDE>  
      --idx <IDX>          Path to kodex.idx (default: .scalex/kodex.idx, or `KODEX_IDX` env var)
  -h, --help               Print help